content: --अंत {%<ab>a.</ab>%} bringing to an end, terminating. (--तः {1} Yama, the god of death. द्वितीयं कृतांतमिवाटंतं व्याधमपश्यत् <ls>H. 1.</ls> {2} fate, destiny; क्रूरस्तस्मिन्नपि न सहते संगमं नो कृतांतः <ls>Me. 105.</ls> {3} a demonstrated conclusion. dogma, a proved doctrine. {4} a sinful or inauspicious action. {5} an epithet of Saturn. {6} Saturday. {7} the inevitable result of former actions. {8} the second lunar mansion. {9} the number ‘two.’
